><a aria-label="Latest" class="_78f6f _15367" href="/latest/">Latest</a><div class="ec54f _92064" data-module-name="nav-latest-dropdown"></div></li><li class="f6f23 _4321c" data-module-name="nav-obsessions-cell"><a aria-label="Obsessions" class="_78f6f _4321c" href="/obsessions/">Obsessions</a><div class="b31c6 _92064" data-module-name="nav-obsessions-dropdown"></div></li><li class="f6f23 _31dd4" data-module-name="nav-featured-cell"><a aria-label="Featured" class="_78f6f _31dd4" href="/featured/">Featured</a><div class="ac77e _92064" data-module-name="nav-featured-dropdown"></div></li><li class="f6f23 _62f60" data-module-name="nav-quartz-logo-cell"><a aria-label="Quartz home" class="_78f6f _62f60" href="/"><svg class="_92252 quartz" width="160" height="26" viewBox="619 14 160 26" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M778.978 19.335l-12.863 15.356h12.863v3.902H761.05v-4.106l12.909-15.152h-12.013v-3.811h17.033v3.811m-26.298-3.85v3.85h-7.174v19.258h-3.884V19.335h-7.172v-3.85h18.23m-30.853 15.282a8.023 8.023 0 0 0 4.447-7.177c0-4.236-3.478-8.02-7.81-8.105h-8.52v23.108h3.885v-6.959h3.52l8.009 8.147 2.7-2.678-6.23-6.336zm-3.644-2.946h-4.354v-8.462h4.354c2.368 0 4.296 1.897 4.296 4.232s-1.928 4.23-4.296 4.23zm-25.471-12.336h-4.664l-8.868 23.108h4.071l1.662-4.502h10.937l1.66 4.502h4.072l-8.87-23.108zm-6.32 15.004l3.992-10.43 3.985 10.43h-7.977zM671.66 15.485v14.619c0 4.956-4.01 8.987-8.945 8.987-4.934 0-8.949-4.032-8.949-8.987V15.485h3.881v14.619c-.085 2.854 2.226 5.175 5.07 5.175 2.837 0 5.148-2.321 5.092-5.175V15.485h3.851m-30.186 18.679a12.076 12.076 0 0 0 2.344-7.167c0-6.675-5.415-12.112-12.062-12.112-6.653 0-12.062 5.437-12.062 12.112 0 6.681 5.409 12.112 12.062 12.112 2.614 0 5.039-.838 7.017-2.267l3.024 3.035 2.684-2.692-3.007-3.021zm-2.729-2.74l-4.457-4.475-2.681 2.697 4.434 4.45a8.204 8.204 0 0 1-4.284 1.202c-4.561 0-8.268-3.721-8.268-8.3 0-4.574 3.707-8.3 8.268-8.3 4.553 0 8.265 3.725 8.265 8.3a8.29 8.29 0 0 1-1.277 4.427z" fill-rule="evenodd" fill="var(--c